@startuml
title E6-01 — Propose and Approve Debt Transaction\nReturn, Correct and Resubmit Sequence

hide footbox
autonumber "<b>[00]"

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam maxMessageSize 35

skinparam ParticipantPadding 55
skinparam BoxPadding 25

skinparam sequence {
  ArrowThickness 1.2
  ParticipantFontSize 14
  ActorFontSize 14
  MessageFontSize 13
  LifeLineBorderColor Black
}

actor "Issuance\nOfficer" as Officer

box "Debt Issuance Platform"
  boundary "Transaction\nWorkspace" as Workspace
  control "Validation\nService" as Validation
  control "Approval\nWorkflow" as Workflow
  database "Transaction and\nAudit Repository" as Repository
end box

actor "Treasury\nApprover" as Approver

== Review Submitted Proposal ==

Approver -> Workflow : Open submitted\nproposal

Workflow -> Repository : Retrieve submitted\nversion and history

Repository --> Workflow : Terms, validation\nand prior changes

Workflow --> Approver : Present approval\npackage

Approver -> Workflow : Return for changes\nwith reason

Workflow -> Repository : Record return decision\nStatus = Changes Required

Repository --> Workflow : Decision recorded

Workflow --> Officer : Notify changes required

note over Officer, Approver
Return reason should be
specific enough to support
a clear correction.
end note

== Correct Proposal ==

Officer -> Workspace : Open returned\ntransaction

Workspace -> Repository : Retrieve editable\nworking version

Repository --> Workspace : Returned terms\nand approver comments

Workspace --> Officer : Display correction\nrequirements

Officer -> Workspace : Update transaction\nterms

Workspace -> Repository : Save revised draft\nas new version

Repository --> Workspace : New version saved

== Revalidate ==

Officer -> Workspace : Request validation

Workspace -> Validation : Validate revised\nterms

Validation -> Repository : Read rules,\nlimits and references

Repository --> Validation : Current rules\nand limits

alt Revised proposal is valid

  Validation --> Workspace : Valid

  Workspace --> Officer : Validation passed

else Revised proposal is still invalid

  Validation --> Workspace : Validation errors

  Workspace --> Officer : Display errors

  note over Officer, Workspace
  Officer corrects remaining
  issues before resubmission.
  end note

end

== Resubmit ==

Officer -> Workspace : Submit revised\nproposal

Workspace -> Workflow : Create new\napproval request

Workflow -> Repository : Lock revised version\nStatus = Submitted

Repository --> Workflow : Version recorded

Workflow --> Approver : Notify resubmission

== Approve Revised Version ==

Approver -> Workflow : Review revised\nproposal

Workflow -> Repository : Retrieve current and\nprior versions

Repository --> Workflow : Revised terms and\nchange comparison

Workflow --> Approver : Present revision\nsummary

Approver -> Workflow : Approve revised\ntransaction

Workflow -> Repository : Record approval\nStatus = Approved

Repository --> Workflow : Approval recorded

Workflow --> Officer : Revised transaction\napproved

note over Workflow, Repository
Audit history retains:
- original submitted version
- return reason
- revised values
- resubmission
- final approval
end note

@enduml